	<preparation>In a deep covered skillet melt butter and lightly brown meat.  Add vinegar, lemon juice, worchester sauce, celery, onion, catsup and mix well.  Bring to a simmer and add tomato soup, sugar, garlic, salt and water.  Cover and simmer for 60 minutes.

If mixture is still a bit moist at the end of an hour, uncover and allow water to cook off.</preparation>
